---
import Landing from "../layouts/Landing.astro";
---

<Landing title="Terms of Service | Drobu" description="Terms of Service for Drobu clipboard manager for macOS.">
  <main id="main" class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8">Terms of Service</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-sm max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
      <p><strong class="text-text-primary">Last updated:</strong> April 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Pricing</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu is a <strong class="text-text-primary">$14.99 one-time purchase</strong> that includes all updates to Drobu 1.x. Try it free for <strong class="text-text-primary">14 days</strong> before paying. Full functionality during the trial, no payment method required upfront. Payments are handled by <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline">Stripe</a>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Refunds</h2>
      <p>
        Drobu is free to try for <strong class="text-text-primary">14 days</strong> with full functionality and no payment method required &mdash; that's your chance to decide whether it's for you. Because you can fully evaluate Drobu before paying, <strong class="text-text-primary">all sales are final and we don't offer refunds once you purchase</strong>. If something isn't working, email <a href="mailto:support@drobu.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">support@drobu.app</a> and we'll make it right.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">
        EU/UK customers: your license key is delivered immediately on purchase. By buying, you request immediate access to that digital content and acknowledge that you lose your 14-day right of withdrawal once it has been delivered.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">What you get</h2>
      <p>
        A personal license to use Drobu on up to 3 of your Macs. Don't redistribute or reverse-engineer it. Requires macOS 14 (Sonoma) or later.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Your data, your responsibility</h2>
      <p>
        Everything is stored locally on your Mac. We can't access, recover, or back up your clipboard history. Drobu is provided "as is", and we're not liable for data loss.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-text-primary mt-8">Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions? <a href="mailto:support@drobu.app" class="text-accent hover:underline">support@drobu.app</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Landing>
